-------------------------------------------------

@{FG Fill}DATE: 1998/04/06@{FG Text}

April 4th, 1998

@{I}FOR IMMEDIATE RELEASE @{UI}

Contact: @{I}Tammy Lynn Rodley (tammy@asimware.com) @{UI}
@{B}Asimware Innovations Inc.@{UB}
600 Upper Wellington Street, Unit #D
