@{B}Asimware@{UB} is proud to announce today's release of @{B}AsimCDFS v3.9a@{UB}.

This is a maintenance update for the @{B}AsimCDFS v3@{UB} package.

The update highlights include:

Added support for the following drives:

 * @{B}Memorex CRW620@{UB} CD-RW drive
 * @{B}Pioneer 32X@{UB} CD-ROM drive
 * @{B}NEC 4X6@{UB} ATAPI CD-ROM changer
 * @{B}Sony CDU625@{UB} CD-ROM drive
 * @{B}Pinnacle RCD4X4@{UB} CD-R drive
 * @{B}Pinnacle RCD4X12@{UB} CD-R drive
 * @{B}Pinnacle RCDW226@{UB} CD-RW drive

@{B}AsimCDFS v3.9@{UB} also added the following:

 * fixed DosPacket problem

Registered users can obtain this release via our WWW or ftp site.
   ftp: @{B}ftp://ftp.asimware.com@{UB}
   WWW: @{B}http://www.asimware.com@{UB}

You will need your @{B}AsimCDFS@{UB} serial number to obtain access.

The  @{B}AsimCDFS@{UB}  software package is a CD-ROM control system which allows the user
to  read  most  CD-ROM discs with an @{B}Amiga@{UB} computer and a suitable SCSI or ATAPI
CD-ROM drive.

@{B}AsimCDFS@{UB} is equipped with the following advanced features:

 * Access to @{B}ISO 9660@{UB}, @{B}High Sierra@{UB}, @{B}Rock Ridge@{UB} and @{B}Macintosh HFS@{UB} CD-ROM formats.
 * @{B}FishMarket@{UB}, a CD-ROM disc containing the public domain @{B}Fred Fish@{UB} collection.
 * @{B}AsimTunes@{UB},  an  audio  librarian/controller  providing advanced librarian and
   playback features.
 * Support  for  direct digitizing from standard audio CDs and playing audio via
   the @{B}Amiga@{UB} hardware.
 * @{B}CDTV@{UB} and @{B}CD32@{UB} emulation modules, complete with autobooting from CD-ROM discs.
 * Integrated  support for @{B}Kodak@{UB} and @{B}Corel@{UB} PhotoCD discs. Colour @{B}WorkBench@{UB} icons
   are  created for easy identification. Support for resolutions from 192x128 up
   to 3072x2048.
 * Support for both SCSI and ATAPI CD-ROM drives.
 * Preferences editor for all @{B}AsimCDFS@{UB} settings.
 * Full @{B}ARexx@{UB} command set available for all programs.

@{B}Asimware  Innovations  Inc.@{UB}  is  a Canadian software development house providing
innovative  software  solutions  since  1992. We are specialists in DVD, CD-ROM,
CD-R and CD-RW technologies.

