@{FG Shine}AMIGA FOREVER 2.0 IS FINALLY AVAILABLE@{FG Text}
--------------------------------------

@{FG Fill}DATE: 1998/04/14@{FG Text}

@{I}PRESS RELEASE @{UI}

@{B}Amiga Forever 2.0@{UB} is finally available!

Suggested Retail Price                               DM 119.00

US$1.00 = DM 1,81 given today's exchange rates!

@{I}Ordering information: @{UI}

The  most  convenient  method of placing an order is to use our electronic order
form  located  at  @{B}http://www.schatztruhe.de/order.html@{UB}.  You  can  also send an
E-Mail  to  @{I}stefano@schatztruhe.de @{UI} including  your address and the products you
wish to order.

@{B}Amiga  Forever  2.0@{UB} finally began shipping this week. We would like to thank all
customers for their interest and patience in waiting for this release.

@{B}Amiga  Forever 2.0@{UB} includes state of the art software to satisfy two major needs
of  many  @{B}Amiga@{UB} users: to share data between @{B}Amiga@{UB} and other systems, and to use
their  existing  @{B}Amiga@{UB}  software  and  data on non-@{B}Amiga@{UB} hardware. Additionally,
software,  tutorial  and  reference files are included which are likely to be of
interest to any @{B}Amiga@{UB} enthusiast.

@{B}Amiga Forever@{UB} includes hundreds of pages of documentation in HTML and AmigaGuide
formats,  with thousands of useful links and cross references. Both the full and
the upgrade versions of the product contain:

 * Multi-platform  CD-ROM  plus  @{B}Amiga@{UB}  floppy  disk  (to  run  the data sharing
   software on @{B}Amiga@{UB} computers without CD-ROM drive).
 * Exclusive  interview  with @{I}Jay Miner, @{UI}"Father of the @{B}Amiga@{UB}" on topics ranging
   from  the  birth of the @{B}Amiga@{UB} to computers and society, in text format and on
   three audio tracks.
 * @{B}Amiga  Explorer 2.0@{UB} networking software, which allows you to connect an @{B}Amiga@{UB}
   to  one  or  more  @{B}PCs@{UB}, and access @{B}Amiga@{UB} files (including virtual ADF and ROM
   files),  directories  and  volumes  directly  from the @{B}Windows Desktop@{UB}. @{B}Amiga
   Explorer@{UB}  is easier to install and configure than other networking tools, and
   includes  direct  support  for  serial  (null  modem)  cable  connections, in
   addition to TCP/IP.
 * @{B}MSH@{UB}  filing  system  to  allow  all  @{B}Amiga@{UB} computers to read and write @{B}MS-DOS@{UB}
   floppy disks.
 * Officially  licensed  @{B}Amiga ROM@{UB} and @{B}OS@{UB} files from version 1.0 to version 3.0,
   to be used for @{B}Amiga@{UB} emulation.
 * @{B}UAE  Amiga@{UB}  emulator  for  @{B}Windows@{UB} and @{B}DOS@{UB}, and @{B}Fellow@{UB} for @{B}DOS@{UB}. All emulation
   support  files (@{B}Amiga ROM@{UB} and @{B}OS@{UB}, @{B}Cloanto Amiga@{UB} software, @{B}Picasso 96@{UB} drivers,
   etc.)  can easily be used by other implementations (@{B}Linux@{UB}, @{B}Be@{UB}, @{B}Next@{UB}, etc.) of
   these  emulators, as well as by future new versions. Experimental versions of
   @{B}UAE@{UB} for @{B}PowerPC Amiga@{UB} and @{B}PowerMac@{UB} systems are included.
 * @{B}Picasso  96@{UB}  drivers for the @{B}UAE@{UB} emulation software, supporting palette modes
   up to 256 colors, as well as true color.
 * @{B}Cloanto  Personal Paint 7.1@{UB} (paint, animation and image processing software),
   @{B}DirDiff  5.1@{UB} (file synchronization and replication software) and @{B}AmiToRTF 4.2@{UB}
   (to convert texts from @{B}Amiga@{UB} to @{B}Windows@{UB} formats), usable on a "real" @{B}Amiga@{UB} as
   well as in the emulation environment.
 * @{B}Amiga   Interactive  Guide@{UB},  by  @{I}Gareth  Knight: @{UI} an  encyclopedia  of  @{B}Amiga@{UB}
   technology, history and opinions.
 * All  upgrades  and  extensions  for @{B}Windows@{UB} and @{B}DOS@{UB} required by the emulation
   software:  @{B}Service  Pack  3@{UB}  for @{B}Windows NT 4.0@{UB}, @{B}DirectX@{UB} for @{B}Windows 95@{UB}, @{B}VESA@{UB}
   shareware software for @{B}DOS@{UB} and @{B}Windows@{UB}.
 * Tutorials  and  FAQs  on data sharing, emulation, floppy disks, serial links,
   TCP/IP, @{B}UAE@{UB}, @{B}Fellow@{UB} and much more.

